{{Otheruses|Butter}}
'''Blue butter''' was a type of [[Butter/Legends|butter]]. It could be a topping on [[Foodstuff|butter pastries]].<ref name="Mercy Kill">''[[X-Wing: Mercy Kill]]''</ref> The softness of [[Leather/Legends|leather]] could be compared to it.<ref name="Exile">''[[Legacy of the Force: Exile]]''</ref> The ease of a task could also be compared to a [[Vibroknife/Legends|vibroknife]] through blue butter.<ref name="Rebel Stand">''[[The New Jedi Order: Enemy Lines II: Rebel Stand]]''</ref>

